{
  "text": "General methods. Experiments were repeated at least twice with similar results. Synthesis of MTX poly(g-glutamate) metabolites [CITATION_1] and protein [i.e., dihydrofolate reductase (DHFR)]-bound MTX (18) were quantitated as described. Reversed-phase analytic high-performance liquid chromatography was done as described [CITATION_2] .",
